!! Detailed Cost Breakdown

!!! Year 1: Foundation ($120,000-200,000)
* **Prior Art Analysis:** $25,000-40,000
* **US Provisional Applications:** $12,000-20,000
* **PCT Applications:** $32,000-48,000
* **Trademark Filings:** $15,000-30,000
* **Legal Counsel Retainer:** $36,000-60,000

!!! Year 2: Global Filing ($100,000-180,000)
* **National Phase Entries:** $60,000-120,000
* **Prosecution Responses:** $25,000-40,000
* **Additional Applications:** $15,000-20,000

!!! Year 3: Prosecution & Maintenance ($80,000-150,000)
* **Ongoing Prosecution:** $40,000-80,000
* **Patent Maintenance:** $15,000-30,000
* **Additional Filings:** $25,000-40,000

